/a>;也在游戏中播出。该活动用于启动&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/1/24283508/fortnite-remix-chapter-2-concert-snoop-dogg-ice-spice&quot;>;重新混合了大逃杀第二章的迷你赛季&lt;/a>;。现在，我们又迎来了另一场虚拟音乐会，尽管这场音乐会看起来更类似于《堡垒之夜》过去的音乐活动，比如那些以 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge. com/2021/8/9/22616664/ariana-grande-fortnite-rift-tour-worldbuilding-storytelling&quot;>;爱莉安娜·格兰德&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2020/4/23/21233637/travis-scott-fortnite-concert-astronomical-live-report&quot;>;特拉维斯·斯科特&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id =&quot;0UmDkV&quot;>;它被称为 Remix：The Finale，最大的区别似乎是规模。此次活动将邀请四位艺术家，而不是一位艺术家：Snoop、Ice Spice、Eminem 和 Juice WRLD。所有这些都出现在本赛季的游戏中 (&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/12/2/23978521/fortnite-the-big-bang-eminem-chapter-5&quot;>;阿姆还举办了自己的个人活动...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/30/24308372/fortnite-remix-finale-concert-juice-wrld-chapter-6-how-to-watch&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a >; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/30/24308372/fortnite-remix-finale-concert-juice-wrld-chapter-6-how-to-watch" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/30/24308372/fortnite-remix-finale-concert-juice-wrld-chapter-6-how-to-watch</id><author><name>安德鲁·韦伯斯特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-30T08:38:52-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-30T08:38:52-05:00</updated><title> Max、Hulu 和 Paramount Plus 都在黑色星期五周末大幅打折</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Max 徽标的矢量插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Cj0ywk9y5UX2gMixg2HExdjE7LM=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73749908/STK055_HBOMAX__D.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;插图由 Cath Virginia / The Verge 绘制&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;nGcPWA&quot;>;如果您想了解最近的节目和电影 - 包括&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/16/24158479/the-anjin-is-probabilly-coming-back-for-even-more-seasons-of-shogun&quot;>;&lt;em>;幕府将军&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;、&lt;